Package: bowen.biodiversity.data
Title: Data Processing for Bowen Island Biodiversity
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Jay", "Matsushiba", , "hello@jmatsushiba.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Data ETL pipeline for processing biodiversity data for
    Bowen Island conservation planning and spatial prioritization analysis.
    This package prepares species distribution models, habitat richness maps,
    and threat assessments to inform conservation decision-making for the
    Bowen Island Municipality.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Palen-Lab/bowen.biodiversity.webapp
